COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent
v.
Kathleen Granahan KANE, Petitioner No. 414 MAL 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. November 26, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 26th day of November, 2018, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is DENIED.

Movant Stan J. Caterbone's "Request to Appear Pro Se and to File an Amicus Curiae Brief" in support of petitioner is DENIED.
